### GET all flowers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/flowers
Accept: application/json

### POST new flower
POST http://localhost:8080/api/flowers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flowerType": "ROSE",
  "color": "RED",
  "price": 60.0,
  "sepalLength": 15.0
}

### Search flowers by price
GET http://localhost:8080/api/flowers/search?maxPrice=40.0
Accept: application/json

### Test payment with credit card
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payment/credit-card
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardNumber": "1234567812345678",
  "expiryDate": "12/25",
  "cvv": "123",
  "amount": 100.0
}

### Test PayPal payment
